呢個係香港人既戰役<br />\n冇玩膠既價值"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:43:27.000Z","msg":"TRUTH 必須推！！！ 唔好再玩膠"},{"pid":"6d322f5a1460243e32070d14d62a8cdf5646459f","tid":1412932,"uid":706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n唔好幫對家將我地既憤怒轉做歡笑"},{"pid":"53aa376bb91dce0809854ef356d1b744b18c5fbe","tid":1412932,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:45:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"49c94ea2c3a93609e7c016ccba978f04aadb6c39","tid":1412932,"uid":98139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暫停對所有政府記者會進步惡攪膠化 以免轉移焦點</span></strong>"},{"pid":"016b06020102c4b785a1e5a5a41008d3f38bbbf6","tid":1412932,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:47:27.000Z","msg":"其實點解狗狗記者會我地咁驚呢<br />\n我覺得係CCTVB加日日開，瘋狂Cut黎Cut去，去洗腦<br />\n好容易令人成日focus左過去<br />\n不過而家記者咁強勢都叫好啲，仲有民間記者會幫手反駁<br />\n<br />\n但係而家因為已經唔係14年，唔係日日佔領<br />\n佢日日都唔一定有野講，所以而家瘋狂做埋啲鳩屎野<br />\n引哂你地啲人出黎，咁先有野講<br />\n<br />\n應對：<br />\n其實我覺得最好就係冷處理佢，當佢冇到<br />\n不過大前提係CCTVB要執粒先<br />\n<br />\n所以一定要加強抵制CCTVB，加強文宣<br />\n要改變文宣策略，要學下英國脫歐嗰套電影<br />\n其實都好多Post都有講過，不過再講下"},{"pid":"f219173dc238e66ce411f0629749529eea9a57c1","tid":1412932,"uid":6528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雙普選一定要排最頭，仲要好似美國咁設時限係2020年之前落實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙普選設時限，為港獨正名，不能無了期五大訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1434739\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1434739</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n當新移民夠多，雙普選自然會落實，港共明顯會用偽民主反真港人<br />\n（雖然係舊post，但都想人諗下，一定要止左血先）<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1328467\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1328467</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n想比更多人知道其實而家呢一刻基本上得番<span style=\"color: gold;\">香港獨立</span>呢條路，<br />\n我知好多人未準備好，我知而家急唔黎。<br />\n但係想大家思考下，種下一個思想，唔好屌我住。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家就算有真普選其實都係under中共！！<br />\n咁唔通去到2047再抗爭過咩，西方國家都出唔到手幫你地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為白紙黑字寫明50年，西方國家唔好話出手，連發聲既正當性都冇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能好多前人都係到諗點解英國當時唔寫999年！<br />\n可能好多我地呢代既諗點解上一代冇去抗爭！<br />\n可能好多下一代係2047係到諗點解我地唔直接爭取獨立！！！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以好似上一代咁，計好哂數50年後都死左啦，唔好理啦。<br />\n我地唔可以再咁自私啦，過埋2047都嗰頭近啦，之後再算啦。<br />\n我想我地既下一代唔需要再為呢啲事再受苦啦，我只係希望下一代可以係呼吸住自由既空氣出世係呢個地球上。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所有既問題，所有既恩怨，係我地呢代到解決哂啦，好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有問題去到最後只會追究到主權問題，希望大家思考下。<br />\n今次搞到咁大真係最後一次反擊同最大力量。<br />\n<br />\nBTW，五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n雙普選應要排最頭，仲要設時限，最好2020年之前！"},{"pid":"b8ac88efa14d889e1750c78c8ba2830b19261c5d","tid":1412932,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"正視"},{"pid":"561aa42c5cb07900477fe13b84a586482ce28942","tid":1412932,"uid":269694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:50:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bfc6ba3ec524765aad5e89ac8c7818d5b8678386","tid":1412932,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:52:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【和你飛】機場集會文宣資源集合<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1435960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1435960</a></span>"},{"pid":"3e42e4ceb764e74f6a767cecd53c775091d7e49c","tid":1412932,"uid":100267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"好重要，推"},{"pid":"3082f660470f0fdc01af4746dd4f6d678d17c4da","tid":1412932,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"唔想再輸"},{"pid":"3483a34598da991c1eb375032cb2a3b2ed25a264","tid":1412932,"uid":109437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"立場都係<br />\n民間記者會又唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eecc2b74006177421ebba3261b15240c71341873","tid":1412932,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"推撚到每個人都睇到"},{"pid":"561463fa8dc64c7b35ee492775e0be37c2995c63","tid":1412932,"uid":199257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5442ca1ee9c8862a7cee996dc6ac3da4b08549","tid":1412932,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:04:55.000Z","msg":"唔可以再輸"},{"pid":"9f3f7aa470b72305b3869f6484898eab094337c2","tid":1412932,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:07:26.000Z","msg":"推撚到每個人都睇到"},{"pid":"15fad6eca5071b32f136ad1003cf2a94e4ea0a95","tid":1412932,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:07:43.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n唔好幫佢地宣傳<br />\n係宣傳都集中民間記者會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f89475059dd479bc941c30883aec831fc8ad76","tid":1412932,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:08:41.000Z","msg":"推!!不膠化, 冷處理!!"},{"pid":"dcb2e0be64f921847cb07e062f6ee620e268e52f","tid":1412932,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:10:19.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"af91a155cd0339500ddc8914b552c3ffca78b2d2","tid":1412932,"uid":289124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:18:31.000Z","msg":"媒體我唔期望太多，而且對政府黎講就算淨得cctvb一間播都夠做。<br />\n我地自己爭氣啲，推多啲正經post，少啲飛機恥笑post<br />\n<br />\npush"},{"pid":"6d50e1699d2c67f8756c6af1116e38cdeb7861b1","tid":1412932,"uid":258770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:18:47.000Z","msg":"冷處理"}]}